\c 18
\s Kuwirirana kwaJonatani naDhavhidhi
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika paakapedza kutaura naSauro, kuti mweya waJonatani wakasunganidzwa pamweya waDhavhidhi\x + Gen.. 44.30.\x*; Jonatani ndokumuda semweya wake\x + 18.3. 19.2. 20.17. 2 Sam. 1.26. Det. 13.6.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino Sauro wakamutora nezuva iro, akasazomutendera kudzokera kumba kwababa vake\x + 17.15.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino Jonatani naDhavhidhi vakaita sungano, nokuti wakamuda semweya wake.
\v 4 Jonatani ndokukurura jazi raaiva akapfeka ndokuripa kuna Dhavhidhi, nezvipfeko zvake, kusvika kumunondo wake, uye kusvika kuuta hwake, uye kusvika kubhanhire rake.
\p
\v 5 Dhavhidhi ndokubuda kuenda kwose Sauro kwaaimutuma, akazvibata neuchenjeri; Sauro ndokumuisa pamusoro pevarume vehondo; akava wakanaka pameso evanhu vose, uyewo pameso evaranda vaSauro.
\p
\v 6 Zvino zvakaitika pakusvika kwavo, Dhavhidhi paakadzoka pakuuraya muFirisitia, kuti vakadzi vakabuda kumaguta ose aIsraeri vachiimba uye vachitamba kuchingamidza mambo Sauro\x + Eki. 15.20. Vato. 11.34. Vato. 21.21.\x* nengoma, nemufaro, uye nezviridzwa\x + Eki. 15.20. Vato. 11.34. Vato. 21.21.\x*.
\v 7 Vakadzi ndokubvumirana vachitamba ndokuti\x + 21.11. Eki. 15.21.Num.. 21.17.\x*: Sauro wakauraya zvuru zvemazana ake\x + 21.11. 29.5.\x*, asi Dhavhidhi makumi ezvuru ake.
\v 8 Sauro ndokutsamwa kwazvo, uye shoko iri raiva rakaipa pameso ake, iye ndokuti: Vapa kuna Dhavhidhi makumi ezvuru zvemazana, asi kwandiri zvuru; wasarirwa neumambo hwoga\x + 15.28.\x*?
\v 9 Zvino Sauro wakagodora Dhavhidhi kubva pazuva iroro zvichienda mberi.
\p
\v 10 Zvino zvakaitika chifume kuti mweya wakaipa waMwari wakauya pamusoro paSauro nesimba\x + 16.14. Vato. 9.23.\x*, iye ndokuporofita mukati meimba\x + 19.24. 1 Madz. 18.29. Mab. 16.16.\x*; Dhavhidhi ndokuridza neruoko rwake sepane dzimwe nguva\x + 16.16.\x*; zvino maiva nepfumo muruoko rwaSauro\x + 19.9.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino Sauro wakapotsera pfumo, ndokuti: Ndichabaira Dhavhidhi nepamadziro\x + 20.33. 19.10.\x*. Asi Dhavhidhi wakanzvenga kaviri kubva pamberi pake.
\p
\v 12 Zvino Sauro wakatya Dhavhidhi\x + 18.29,15.\x* nokuti Jehovha waiva naye\x + 16.18.\x* uye waiva abva kuna Sauro\x + 16.14. 28.15.\x*.
\v 13 Naizvozvo Sauro wakamubvisa kwaari, ndokumuisa kuva mukuru wechuru wake; zvino akabuda nekupinda pamberi pevanhu\x + 18.16. Num.. 27.17. 2 Sam. 5.2.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakazvibata neuchenjeri panzira dzake dzose, Jehovha ndokuva naye\x + 18.12.\x*.
\v 15 Sauro paakaona kuti anozvibata neuchenjeri kwazvo, ndokumutya.
\v 16 Asi Israeri wose naJudha vakada Dhavhidhi, nokuti waibuda nekupinda pamberi pavo\x + 18.5.\x*.
\s Dhavhidhi anowana Mikari mukunda waSauro
\p
\v 17 Zvino Sauro wakati kuna Dhavhidhi: Tarira, mukunda wangu mukuru Merabhi\x + 14.49.\x*, ndichamupa kwauri kuva mukadzi\x + 14.49.\x*; koga iva mhare kwandiri, ugorwa hondo dzaJehovha\x + 25.28. 17.47.\x*. Nokuti Sauro wakati: Ruoko rwangu ngarurege kuva pamusoro pake, asi ruoko rweVaFirisitia ngaruve pamusoro pake\x + 18.21,25.\x*.
\v 18 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakati kuna Sauro: Ndini ani, uye upenyu hwangu chii, \add ne\add*mhuri yababa vangu kwaIsraeri, kuti ndive mukwasha wamambo\x + 18.23. 2 Sam. 7.18.\x*?
\v 19 Asi zvakaitika panguva Merabhi mukunda waSauro yaaizopiwa kuna Dhavhidhi, kuti iye wakapiwa kuna Adhirieri\x + 2 Sam. 21.8.\x* muMehorati kuva mukadzi\x + Vato. 7.22.\x*.
\v 20 Zvino Mikari mukunda waSauro waida Dhavhidhi; zvino vakaudza Sauro, nyaya iyi ndokuva yakarurama pameso ake\x + 18.28. 14.49.\x*.
\v 21 Sauro ndokuti: Ndichamupa iye, kuti ave musungo kwaari\x + Eki. 10.7.\x*, uye kuti ruoko rweVaFirisitia rwumurwise\x + 18.17.\x*. Naizvozvo Sauro wakati kuna Dhavhidhi: Kechipiri uchava mukwasha wangu\x + 18.26.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Zvino Sauro wakaraira varanda vake \add achiti\add*: Tauriranai naDhavhidhi pakavanda muchiti: Tarira, mambo anofara mauri, nevaranda vake vose vanokuda; naizvozvo ikozvino chiva mukwasha wamambo.
\v 23 Zvino varanda vaSauro vakataura mashoko awo munzeve dzaDhavhidhi. Dhavhidhi ndokuti: Chinhu chakareruka pameso enyu here kuva mukwasha wamambo, zvandiri munhu murombo uye anozvidzika\x + Num.. 16.9.\x*?
\v 24 Varanda vaSauro ndokumuudza vachiti: Dhavhidhi wataura semashoko awa.
\v 25 Sauro ndokuti: Muchataura saizvozvo kuna Dhavhidhi: Mambo haashuvi roora, asi zvikanda zvepamberi zana zveVaFirisitia\x + Gen.. 34.12.\x*, kuti kutsiviwe vavengi vamambo\x + 14.24.\x*. Asi Sauro wakafunga kuita Dhavhidhi awe neruoko rweVaFirisitia\x + 18.17.\x*.
\v 26 Varanda vake pavakaudza Dhavhidhi mashoko awa, nyaya yakava yakanaka pameso paDhavhidhi kuva mukwasha wamambo\x + 18.20.\x*. Asi mazuva aiva asati azadzisika\x + 18.21.\x*.
\v 27 Naizvozvo Dhavhidhi wakasimuka ndokuenda iye nevarume vake, ndokuuraya varume mazana maviri pakati peVaFirisitia\x + 18.13.\x*; Dhavhidhi ndokuuya nezvikanda zvavo zvepamberi, ndokuzvipa zvakakwana kuna mambo, kuti ave mukwasha wamambo. Sauro ndokumupa Mikari mukunda wake kuva mukadzi\x + 2 Sam. 3.14.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Zvino Sauro wakaona uye wakaziva kuti Jehovha waiva naDhavhidhi. Mikari mukunda waSauro ndokumuda\x + 18.12.\x*.
\v 29 Zvino Sauro waiva achiri kutyazve Dhavhidhi\x + 2 Sam. 3.14.\x*; uye Sauro wakava muvengi waDhavhidhi mazuva ose\x + 2 Madz. 13.3.\x*.
\v 30 Zvino machinda eVaFirisitia akabuda\x + 19.8. 2 Sam. 11.1.\x*, zvikaitika kuti pose paaibuda Dhavhidhi waizvibata neuchenjeri kupfuura varanda vose vaSauro, kusvika zita rake rakurumbira kwazvo\x + 18.5.\x*.